&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Associate Manager, Marketing Web Strategy will be responsible for briefing, executing, reporting, and optimizing web experiences across the Peloton ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Partner with cross-functional teams across Marketing, Product, and Engineering to deliver web experiences that drive Member acquisition.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;ABOUT THE ROLE&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Device Services team owns the connected-device backend platform that powers the Peloton Bike, Tread, and Guide hardware fleet.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHAT YOU&#39;LL DO&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Design and build full-stack services in TypeScript and Go to operate millions of connected devices in production.&lt;/p&gt;
